Perfect fit. Perfect fabric. Perfect for every day.™

A fan favourite with a reputation as the hoodie of all hoodies, this is a pullover sweatshirt with a kanga pocket, dropped shoulders and ribbed trim. It’s made with Aritzia's Cozy Sweatfleece — premium midweight fleece famous for its soft-brushed back, sueded face and cloud-nine plush feel. The best kind of cozy. This version features an exclusive chenille arched text graphic that was designed in house.
